              "coded_information": {
                "nuclide": "10-NE-22",
                "field_identifier": "ENR",
                "value": 0.99
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The 22Ne targets were produced by",
                "implantation of enriched Ne onto think tantalum",
                "backing with dimensions of 3.8 cm x 3.8 cm. The",
                "implantation profile of the 22Ne targets was",
                "investigated using the 1278-keV resonance in the",
                "22Ne(p,g) 23Na reaction"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "NAICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Gamma rays were detected using HECTOR array,",
                "consisting of 16 NaI(Tl) crystals with two phototubes",
                "attached to each crystal. The crystals are arranged in",
                "a frame to form a cube 16 x 16 x 16 in. in dimension.",
                "The center of the detector array consists of a 60-mm",
                "borehole that allows the target to be placed at the",
                "center giving a 4Pi total coverage for the detection",
                "of gamma rays."
              ]
            }
